"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"奈央","body":"動作有確實記牢了，接下來只剩在A區決賽前\n繼續練得更熟……應該是這樣","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"thinking01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event267-01-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"怎麼感覺是很～微妙的說詞啊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event267-01-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":226}],"windowDisplayName":"奈央","body":"嗯～……表現當然不錯的啦。\nA區決賽的課題『要傳給觀眾的訊息』……\n以及感謝的心情我覺得的確是有融入到演奏中","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":226,"motionName":"thinking01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":226,"voiceId":"event267-01-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻彌","body":"我也是，我知道現在的演出呈現很穩定，\n但奈央小姐有點在意的心情，我隱約地好像也能懂","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"thinking01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event267-01-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterI